		| `[0, 255]` | ![linear gradient blue to green with ratios 0 and 255](/images/gradient-ratios-2.jpg) |
		| `[127, 255]` | ![linear gradient blue to green with ratios 127 and 255](/images/gradient-ratios-3.jpg) |

